This #collaboration with Toki has made my weekends fun!
What’s your favorite weekend plan? Well, mine is to chill by the pool with my friends, good food and ofcourse @suntorytoki! 
In Japanese, Toki means time. @suntorytoki brings a vivid blend of luxury, top notch whiskies and bridges the traditional soul of Japan with the contemporary new evolving Japan.
It has a light body and tastes of green tea, honey, and floral notes, and is extremely smooth, you really do feel like you're drinking a whiskey that's distinctly Japanese.
If you’re a whiskey lover who likes the drink to be subtly sweet with a hint of vanilla oak, white pepper and ginger then you might probably love this.
 
#drinkresponsibly

With my girl @bosslady_pritikakapoor
